puppet

This is the puppet module.

This module will install and mange puppet on RedHat/CentOS and Ubuntu hosts.

It will:
1) Add puppetlabs yum or apt repo
2) Install the latest puppet packages and augeas
3) Configure and manage clients and masters

Use it in a node def or in a class def as:
# Install a puppet client:
puppet::client {puppetclient: puppetserver => "somehost.domain.tld"}

# Install a puppet master
puppet::master {puppetmaster: puppetserver => "somehost.domain.tld"}


